sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant API as Presentation API
    participant BL as Business Logic
    participant DB as Persistence Database
    participant Email as ConfirmationEmail

    User->>API: Fill out registration form
    API->>BL: Submit user data (API call)
    BL->>DB: Create user record
    DB-->>BL: Confirm storage
    BL->>Email: Trigger welcome email
    Email-->>User: Send confirmation email
    BL-->>API: Return success response
    API-->>User: Show "Welcome" message
